## Minimum Software Requirements

Below are the requirements for running the engine or editor.

(#MinSoftwareReqs)

[PUBLISH:Licensee]
| Running the Engine ||
| -------- | --- |
| **Operating System** | Microsoft Windows Vista/7 64-bit |
| **DirectX Version** | [DirectX End-User Runtimes (June 2010)](http://www.microsoft.com/download/en/details.aspx?id=8109) |
| **Visual C++ Runtimes** | [Microsoft Visual C++ 2013 Redistributables](http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=40784) |

[REGION:note]
**Note:** Running the `UE4PrereqSetup.msi` found in `//depot/UE4/Engine/Extras/Redist/en-us` will install software necessary to run Unreal Engine, such as the DirectX and VC++ runtimes mentioned above.
[/REGION]
[/PUBLISH:Licensee]

